==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Horsehair
<hw>Horse"hair`</hw> <pr>(h⟦ocir⟧rs"h⟦acir⟧r`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>A hair of a horse, especially one from the mane or tail; the hairs
of the mane or tail taken collectively;</def>
<specif>Specifically:</specif> <def>a black shiny fabric made of such
hairs, used commonly in the 1800's as a covering for stuffed furniture
such as chairs and couches.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Horsehair worm</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>the hair
worm or gordius.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Horsehead</ent>⟦br⟧
